ut fine-tuning."}, {"problem": "Policy code generation systems can be brittle to changes in API formats and to previously unseen, task-specific skills, hindering deployment across varied robotic configurations.", "method": "RoboPro employs an extendable API library with explicit perception (Lper) and control (Lcon) abstractions and detailed in-context prompts that define function semantics, parameterization, and usage while avoiding hardcoding. This design teaches the model to internalize atomic skills from API definitions, improving robustness to API Renaming and Refactoring, with minimal performance drop on RLBench. It also zero-shot adapts to new task-specific APIs for compositional tasks (e.g., Water Plants, Hit Ball, Scoop Cube), outperforming CaP and GPT-4o on these unseen skill sets."}]}
